{
  "text": "Returning to the main proof, it suffices to prove that there exist polynomials q n 's for all n ≥ 1 such that for each N ≥ 1 the following properties (H1), (H2), and (H3) hold true: [CITATION_1] where the numbers δ * n,α 's, for α ≥ 1/2, are defined recursively by",
